headline: Realtor.com® Forecasts the 10 Best Markets for First-Time Homebuyers in 2025
summary: For first-time homebuyers, the Mid-Atlantic and Florida are the best places to kickstart their home ownership journey in 2025. That's according to the 2025 Realtor.com® Best Markets for First-Time Homebuyers report, which ranked Harrisburg, Penn., as No. 1 followed by Rochester, N.Y., Villas, Fla., Lauderdale Lakes, Fla., Altamonte Springs, Fla., Lansing, Mich., North Little Rock, Ark., Baltimore, Tonawanda, N.Y., and Wilmington, Del.

headline: Three Reasons to Avoid NWSA and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: News Corp has been treading water for the past six months, recording a small loss of 0.9% while holding steady at $27.47. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 6.1% gain during that period.
